{"word":"G1887 - ἐπαύριον - epaúrion - ep-ow'-ree-on - Day following","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπαύριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epaúrion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ow'-ree-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Day following</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மறுநாள் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"on the morrow"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G839 - αὔριον - aúrion - ow'-ree-on/839\">G839</a>; occuring <i>on</i> the <i>succeeding</i> day, that is, (<a href=\"#/G2250 - ἡμέρα - hēméra - hay-mer'-ah/2250\">G2250</a> being implied) <i>tomorrow:</i> - day following, morrow, next day (after).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}